metadata.name: Wizh Stone #1
metadata.description: Wizh by Soakverse is a collection of 5,000 powerful multi-utility NFTs. Each Wizh Stone gives you access to a multitude of powers in the Soakverse! Possibilities are endless, with jackpots, legendary items, free NFTs & team power boosts during PVP, PVM & Quests! Each Wizh Stone needs to be empowered to provide its lucky owner the full benefit. The Wishing Well will consume that power in exchange for granting you your wish.
